def: The twin flower which grows in cold northern climates.
The act or blazoning; blazoning; emblazonment.
To make a bishop of by consecration. Southey.
A stack or conical pile of hay in the open air.
A combining form, denoting relation to, or dependence upon,natural causes, or the science of physics.
A kind of cast steel containing nickel, which greatly increasesits strength. It is used for armor plate, bicycle tubing, propellershafts, etc.
The name of the Supreme Being, in use among the Arabs and theMohammedans generally.
Of or pertaining to the Annulosa.
In a shrill manner; acutely; with a sharp sound or voice.
A wooden blade with a cross handle, used for mi Tomlinson.
